The New World’s Ugliest Dog Has Just Been Crowned And Her Name Is Martha

And the World’s Ugliest Dog of 2015 is…Martha, a Neapolitan Mastiff. In a competition usually comprised of tiny dogs, the 3-year-old, 125-pound dog beat out 13 other pups to take…
